{
  "stem": "10572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Hamilton, telling her that by the time this letter would reach her, she would know what the crazy deed of a young boy did to all of us, not realizing of course, at that particular point, that by the time she got the letter, that my wording had much more weight than when I wrote it because of the-- what happened to us during the next hours and days and months.",
      "word_count": 71
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mailed the letter at midnight on the 9th of November.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't have a very good night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't get to sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at around 5 o'clock in the morning, there was a-- the doorbell rang.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a knock at the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I looked at my clock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe anybody at 5 o'clock in the morning coming to our house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I put my dressing gown on and went downstairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, who's there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, 'Geheime Staatspolizei,' Gestapo, open the door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And outside were two SS men with a Gestapo agent whom I knew, to whom I had to go whenever I had meetings in my youth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to get his permission.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So Inspector Hemmerling and these two SS men came into our house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Without any formal introduction or so, they just walked in and walked into my father's library and said that they were looking for arms and books, forbidden books and weapons.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the way they went about it, I knew this was nonsense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were not looking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, get your father down here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have to talk to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went upstairs in my parents' bedroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother had an ailing heart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't know how to prepare them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but nevertheless, I told them the Gestapo was downstairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
